title: Eolomea (1972 - East Germany) [multi subs] Eastern Bloc sci fi
description:
Eolomea (1972 - East Germany, Soviet Union, Bulgaria)

Drama / Romance / Science Fiction
 
http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0068542/


Eolomea begins with one of those multi-cultural "general assembly meetings" that are usually convened to discuss what to do about the Mysterians. Scientists and associated bureaucrats on Earth are panicked when they start losing contact with their far-flung network of space stations. Unable to figure out what might be causing this, they take the emergency measure of freezing all space flights. This order sits poorly with cosmonaut Dan Lagny, stationed on a remote outpost with only one other ennui-wracked crewmember for company.
